---
title: Sweet Hoisin Chicken Bowl Seasoned Rice and Soy Mayo
description: There are plenty of flavours and textures going on in tonight's meal!  Togarashi spiced carrots, juicy hoisin chicken, and crisp bok choy. The whole dish comes together with a final drizzle of soy mayo! Simple, convenient, and delicious!
